WEBVTT

00:03:59.372 --> 00:04:01.366
He said, "Yeah, I'm good, 
I'm good."

00:04:01.366 --> 00:04:05.532
We let go, he shook my hand,
said he gave me my respect,

00:04:05.532 --> 00:04:08.903
gave me a cigarette and sent me on my way.

00:04:09.723 --> 00:04:13.464
Believe it or not, you come across
some C.O.s on Rikers Island

00:04:13.464 --> 00:04:16.040
that'll fight you one-on-one.

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:18.247
They feel that they understand how it is,

00:04:18.247 --> 00:04:21.055
and they feel that I'm going
to meet you where you're at.

00:04:21.055 --> 00:04:23.551
Since this is how you commonly
handle your disputes,

00:04:23.551 --> 00:04:25.630
we can handle it in that manner.

00:04:25.630 --> 00:04:28.904
I walk away from it like a man,
you walk away from it like a man,

00:04:28.904 --> 00:04:30.325
and that's it.